Why associate with us?

Entrepreneurs improve the lives of individuals and communities, as well as the overall economy. The benefits of entrepreneurship extend beyond the businesses they establish. For all the benefits entreprenuership offers to individuals, the society and to the country overall, Swayam - E cell, Vasavi College of Engineering is working towards the development of new entreprenuers and fueling their journeys.



We are a group of enthusiastic students who are passionate towards realising the dream of entrepreurship. We actively organise events like e summits, ideathons, etc throughout the year that see huge participation. We have an incubation cell within the campus that has previously seen some great ideas come to life.

What NFL player do you think could be injury-prone based on their playstyle?

For Alumni

Swayam has always been committed to contributing to the very spirit of entreprenuership in various forms. Our distinguished Alumni has firsthand been a part of the rise of Swayam and an audiance to the impact it has created. Swayam continues to innovate new, impactful ideas and ignite passion towatrds entreprenuership in students. For us, in this wonderful journey, the alumni we proudly look up to can act as our mentors and give us expert guidance while inspiring many students of the institution.



Some ways you could get involved with us are -

Mentors

As mentors, you could provide us the right guidance and help us with the right resources. Our students could learn a lot from you along the way and have a successful entreprenuerial journey.

Angel investors

The initial problem most startups face is the phase of collecting funds. Swayam is the birthplace of some great ideas and if your interests align with any of them, you could become an angel investor.

For Students

{/*

What can Swayam offer?

*/}

Students of the institution throughout the academic year will have various opportunities to interact with swayam. One of our flagship events is Ideation Contest where participants pitch their ideas and solve real life problems. Some of these later become a part of our incubation cell.



Swayam has multiple departments that are actively working on organizing events and incubating startups. Students can become part of these departments by participating in Swayam's recruitment events. Swayam takes great pride in all its members and all the work they do.



Swayam can offer you a great peer group; collaborations with whom can lead to fruitful experiences. All of these events might just inspire you to start your entreprenuerial journey or could leave you with loads of memories of a great day spent wonderfully.

For Corporates

We at Swayam work with a clear mission and vision. Swayam's event gallery is a huge repository of many successful and impactful events conducted over the years. Corporates can get involved by giving sponsorships for these events. Swayam's events see huge participation from students and such collaborations can become yeilding experiences for both Swayam and the sponsors.



Entrepreneurship Cell is on the lookout for corporates who can mentor the Business Model that qualify in our competitions. These mentors can help us by providing the right technical guidance and your experiences in the industry can become a boon to us. You could also support some of these ideas by becoming their angel investors.
